{"tid":2298754,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請記錄所有以「候任總統」稱呼拜登嘅媒體","createTime":"2020-11-24T09:17:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T21:00:22.000Z","uid":78971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a226b2f12796ada6534e6509b52ed6721c344f2b","tid":2298754,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:17:44.000Z","msg":"一日比一日少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nNow新聞都轉返用「聲稱勝出選舉嘅」"},{"pid":"277fb2e87a80a4a4b97b00db586dc807ec74b492","tid":2298754,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T19:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05d84519f719c0380c47db01981a9839e0c985c","tid":2298754,"uid":77532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T19:12:27.000Z","msg":"華盛頓再世準總統準偉人拜登"},{"pid":"4cb05fc1710938058d3c62061094760171753c86","tid":2298754,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T19:13:45.000Z","msg":"[11月24號]美國大選新聞總匯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2298532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2298532</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[慎防左膠帶風向］鮑威爾代表美國人控告選舉舞弊，並非代表侵侵團隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2296914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2296914</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n左報話侵律師團輸左三十幾個case , Jenna Ellis  辟謠話係 Fake news<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2296773\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2296773</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[持續慎防五毛左膠帶風向］美國聯邦總務署只提供選舉後財政資助，唔會確認邊個係下屆總統。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2298175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2298175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n《正視聽》GSA署長公開講明自己、家人、同事受到極大人身安全威脅，但依然拒絕承認拜登勝選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2298222\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2298222</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n密切根州聯邦上訴法院批准選舉審查 , 將於星期三上午9點舉行聽證會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2298731\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2298731</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d72f8d6276eff7c9fc84217e8d4163f9f6215085","tid":2298754,"uid":208323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T19:15:18.000Z","msg":"全部都係<br />\n除咗Newsmax OAN"},{"pid":"1d5d3be200361d0ac15831a7f13cbf64b0b2a8c4","tid":2298754,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T21:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}